## Constraints

- Apply both directions of the deletion test — do not skip either.
- Be specific about what complexity would reappear or vanish — give concrete examples, not vague claims.
- If the assessment was Shallow or Very Shallow, the recommendation should reflect that.
- If the module has a single consumer, flag it as an inline candidate.
- Do not execute arbitrary Python code in Jinja2 expressions (sandboxed execution).
- Handle missing variables gracefully (leave as-is or use default if specified).

